# Kill-criteria + paper-equity runtime state. These MUST persist across
# Render cron runs (ephemeral FS → pushed to GitHub, pulled on redeploy).
# Without persistence: the realized-equity anchor resets to 0 daily, the
# hard_kill 7-day window / quarterly clock reset, and the observe-mode
# kill_log audit trail is lost on every redeploy.
!results/kill_state.json
!results/kill_log.jsonl
!results/paper_equity_state.json
